  "title": "Engineering Technician (Urgent Hiring!) [Lentor | 5 days | up to $2800] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Engineering Technician</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Location: Nearest MRT Lentor Singapore 787542 [ Report to office but might need to travel to site]</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: Monday – Friday | 8.30am – 6.15pm</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Salary: $2500 - $2800</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Descriptions:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide direct support to the team leader and engineering staff on daily assignments and projects.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and organize tools and equipment for daily tasks and ensure all necessary materials are available and in good working order.</li>\n  <li>Perform routine maintenance and calibration on a wide range of tools and equipment to ensure optimal performance and longevity.</li>\n  <li>Actively participate in daily housekeeping activities to maintain a clean, safe, and organized workshop and premises. This includes cleaning work areas, storing tools properly, and disposing of waste materials appropriately.</li>\n  <li>Assist in troubleshooting and repair of equipment and systems under the guidance of senior technicians or engineers</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate records of equipment maintenance, repairs, and inventory.</li>\n  <li>Adhere strictly to all safety protocols and procedures, including the use of personal protective equipment (PPE).</li>\n  <li>Collaborate effectively with team members to achieve project goals and maintain a positive work environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Qualifications &amp; Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma/NITEC or equivalent in a related field.</li>\n  <li>Proven experience in a technical or maintenance role.</li>\n  <li>Strong mechanical and technical aptitude, with the ability to use a variety of hand and power tools.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p>\n<p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
